race.description: Masters Of Their Craft Super Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tricky with some likely debutants engaged. CITY GOLD FIELD (1) finished third here over 1400m second up and will be fitter. Maps well again and will be hard to beat. AISLE TWO (9) is also third-up and rates similarly on his 1L defeat here over 1200m. The extra metres suit and he'll be hitting the line hard. ZSA ZSA (4) has ability and resumes off a longish break, well-trialled and switched from Victoria. Wary but needs luck from a wide gate. PLAYBILL (2) is a well-bred debutant who's been a long while coming to the races. Has trialled well enough and on profile deserves a betting watch. Ditto fellow debutants LOVE RUSTLER (10) and SALOON PASSAGE (12), who are both in top metro barns.
